In early [[anthropology]], '''Leiotrichi''' described the [[Race (classification of human beings)|races]] of people distinguished by their smooth [[hair]].<ref>{{Nuttall|inline=1|title=Leiotrichi}}</ref> Races with hair that is not smooth were termed ''Ulotrichi''.

