'''''The Illustrated Guide to the Elements''''' is a book by [[Jenna Whyte]]. Published in 2012, the book features factual information about all the [[chemical elements]] with drawings to illustrate the information. There was mention of a sequel.<ref>http://www.london-artcollege.co.uk/news/2013/04/jenna-whyte-success-story/</ref><ref>http://www.jennawhyte.co.uk/</ref><ref>https://www.amazon.com/The-Illustrated-Guide-Elements-Volume/dp/0957532709/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1377352473&sr=8-1&keywords=jenna+whyte</ref>

